## 1. Overview

{{ product_name | default("OmniSight UVC Camera Module") }} is a USB Video Class 1.5
compliant camera device supporting H.264, MJPEG, and uncompressed YUY2 video output.
Designed for embedded integration, it exposes standard UVC controls plus vendor-specific
extension unit (XU) controls for advanced ISP tuning.

## 2. Features

| Feature | Specification |
