## 5. USB Descriptors

- **Device Descriptor:** USB 2.0 (bcdUSB=0x0200), Class=Misc (0xEF), SubClass=0x02, Protocol=0x01 (IAD)
- **Interface Association Descriptor (IAD):** bFirstInterface=0, bInterfaceCount=2
- **Video Control (VC) Interface:** 1× Camera Terminal, 1× Processing Unit, 1× Extension Unit, 1× Output Terminal
- **Video Streaming (VS) Interface:** H.264 format + MJPEG format + Uncompressed format, multiple frame descriptors per format
- **Still Image Frame Descriptor:** highest resolution JPEG capture
- **Endpoint:** 1× Interrupt EP (VC status), 1× Isochronous/Bulk EP (VS data)

